    CAEN A5818 Linux Driver

    Changelog.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

v1.0.6 (17/04/2026)
-------------------

New features:
- Add support for Ubuntu 26.04, Ubuntu 24.04 HWE, Debian 13, RHEL 10, Fedora
    42 and Fedora 43.
- Drop support for EOL distibutions.

Fixes:
- Fix support for Ubuntu 24.04.


v1.0.5 (19/11/2024)
-------------------

Fixes:
- Add support for RHEL 9.5


v1.0.4 (05/09/2024)
-------------------

Fixes:
- Fix support for DKMS on Fedora


v1.0.3 (20/05/2024)
-------------------

New features:
- Add support for RHEL 9.4


v1.0.2 (07/02/2024)
-------------------

First public release.
